		Issued August 1999. Evaluation Criteria for Reliability-Centered Maintenance (RCM) Processes, SAE JA 1011. www.sae.org&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Nowlan FS, Heap HF,. 1978. Reliability Centered Maintenance, National Technical Information Service, U.S. Department of Commerce, Springfield, Va.&lt;/li&gt;
